# Async consistency

- Route handlers that do I/O: `async def` + async libraries (`aiosqlite`, `httpx.AsyncClient`).
- Never block the event loop inside `async def` (no sync `sqlite3`, `requests`, etc.).
- Tests: `@pytest.mark.anyio` + `httpx.AsyncClient` with `ASGITransport` — not sync `TestClient` for async routes.

This project uses `aiosqlite` + raw SQL repos instead of asyncpg/SQLAlchemy; same principle applies.
